 of interest to scholars and students of bioethics and phenomenological methods in the health and human services"--cProvided by publisher.  a43 0aPain. 0aAging. 0aOlder people. 0aPhenomenology. 0aRoutledge advances in the medical humanities.  aBF 515 M76 2015c1hUAHS-Bi0162035176625  aBF 515 M76 2015wLCc1i0162035176625lON_SHELFmUAHSSp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu10/29/201401ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n2014040955bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/309823301